title: Dolphin Coasters
description: Practical and charming, these unique Dolphin coasters are sure to be a big hit. The set contains four Dolphin coasters, includes a clear hinged box for storage. Makes a nice gift for animal enthusiasts. Each Dolphin coaster is approximately 3.5 x 4.5 inches in size.
